      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "$6,000 - Calling all DIY fans and weekend mechanics! This vehicle is the ultimate project car, offering a fantastic and affordable entry point for someone looking to restore a ride or source quality parts. While it currently shows significant wear and will require a dedicated hand to get it back to its best, it represents a great opportunity to build something special from the ground up!",
