    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is for parts or a major restoration project. The engine suffers from significant mechanical failure and struggles to stay running, while the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping. Externally, the body shows several large dents and rusted panels, and the interior has extensive upholstery damage and non-functional electronics. Prospective buyers should expect to invest considerable time and money into repairs or use it primarily as a donor car.",
